text: Rochefort is a municipality in Boudry in the canton of Neuchâtel in Switzerland. On 1 January 2016, the municipality of Brot-Dessous became part of Rochefort.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 19 January 2016 == Localities == Brot- Dessous, Chambrelien, Champ-du-Moulin, Fretereules, Les Grattes, Montézillon, Rochefort and La Tourne. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Boudry
